Startup:

- roslauch tidyup_demo_launch screen_simulation

The launch files exit normally and "screen -r" opens the started screen sessions.
Robot starts automatically, the rest can be started as normally in a terminal.

Screen windows:
- roscore
- gazebo (robot-sim)
- rviz with a loaded config
- prerequisites (starts all the relevant nodes needed)
- continual_planning (as well as the monitor)

